	Nonfunctional subdomains:

		- anoncvs *
		- bouncer	(times out)
		- distfiles	(support varies between mirrors resolved to)
		- packages	("Empty Page!", self-signed)
		- sources	(times out)

	* Times out


	Fully covered subdomains:

		- (www.)
		- ads
		- archives
		- blogs
		- bugs
		- \d+.bugs
		- council
		- council-webapp
		- dev
		- devmanual
		- foundation
		- forums
		- forums-lb
		- forums-web[12]
		- overlays
